	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah that is correct. It is more commonly called a tilemap <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tile_engine" class="postlink">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tile_engine</a>.  There were few systems that didn't use this kind of setup, the Atari systems at least up to the 7800.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


